# 🇮🇳 India Market Tracker

> Automated **Sensex · Nifty 50 · India VIX** tracker with Telegram alerts and GitHub CSV history.

![GitHub Actions](https://img.shields.io/badge/GitHub_Actions-Automated-blue?logo=github-actions)
![Python](https://img.shields.io/badge/Python-3.11-green?logo=python)
![Data](https://img.shields.io/badge/Data-Yahoo_Finance-purple)

---

## 📦 Files

```
├── market_tracker.py                    ← Main script
├── requirements.txt                     ← Python dependencies
├── data/
│   └── market_history.csv              ← Auto-updated history (committed by bot)
└── .github/
    └── workflows/
        └── market_tracker.yml          ← GitHub Actions (every 5 min)
```

---

## 🚀 Quick Setup

### Step 1 — Fork / Clone this repo

### Step 2 — Create a Telegram Bot

1. Open Telegram → search **@BotFather**
2. Send `/newbot` → follow prompts → copy the **Bot Token**
3. Start a chat with your bot (or add it to a group)
4. Get your **Chat ID**:
   - For personal: visit `https://api.telegram.org/bot<TOKEN>/getUpdates` after sending `/start`
   - For a group: add `@userinfobot` to the group

### Step 3 — Add GitHub Secrets

Go to your repo → **Settings → Secrets and variables → Actions → New repository secret**

| Secret Name          | Value                        |
|----------------------|------------------------------|
| `TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN` | Your bot token from BotFather |
| `TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID`   | Your chat or group ID        |

### Step 4 — Enable GitHub Actions

Go to **Actions tab** → enable workflows if prompted.

### Step 5 — Test it manually

Go to **Actions → India Market Tracker → Run workflow** → set `force_run = true`

---

## 📊 Features

| Feature | Details |
|---|---|
| **Indices** | Sensex (^BSESN), Nifty 50 (^NSEI), India VIX (^INDIAVIX) |
| **Update Frequency** | Every 5 minutes during market hours (Mon–Fri 9:15–15:30 IST) |
| **Drop Alerts** | 🚨 Separate alert if Sensex or Nifty drops ≥1% from previous close |
| **VIX Spike Alert** | 🚨 Alert if India VIX spikes ≥15% in a session |
| **RSI Signal** | Overbought (≥70) / Oversold (≤30) alerts for Nifty 50 |
| **Trend Analysis** | MA5 & MA20 crossover detection |
| **Market Mood** | Strong Bull → Strong Bear sentiment label |
| **CSV History** | Auto-committed to `data/market_history.csv` |
| **Data Source** | Yahoo Finance (free, no API key needed) |

---

## 🌡️ India VIX Safety Zones

| VIX Range | Zone | Interpretation |
|---|---|---|
| < 13 | 🟢 ULTRA LOW | Extreme complacency — reversal risk |
| 13–15 | 🟢 LOW | Calm market — bullish bias |
| 15–18 | 🟡 MODERATE | Normal range — mild caution |
| 18–20 | 🟠 ELEVATED | Volatility picking up |
| 20–25 | 🔴 HIGH | Fear in market — be defensive |
| 25–30 | 🔴 VERY HIGH | Panic zone — sharp swings likely |
| > 30 | ⛔ EXTREME | Crisis / Black Swan territory |

