## 📈 CSV Schema

```
timestamp, sensex, sensex_chg_pct, nifty50, nifty50_chg_pct,
india_vix, vix_zone, nifty_rsi, nifty_trend,
week_chg_nifty, month_chg_nifty
```

---

## ⚙️ Environment Variables

| Variable | Default | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN` | — | Set via GitHub Secret |
| `TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID` | — | Set via GitHub Secret |
| `CSV_PATH` | `data/market_history.csv` | Path for CSV file |
| `FORCE_RUN` | `false` | Set to `true` to bypass market hours check |

